snippet.title: RetroGamingNow
snippet.description:
Welcome to RetroGamingNow! I used to be a let's play channel, but recently I've moved towards the video essay format. Send me an email below if you want to get into contact with me!

Disclaimer: This channel is in no way aimed towards children or anyone under the age of 13. The language of the videos on this channel is not intended for children to understand. This channel does not include activities that appeal to children, such as play-acting, simple songs or games, or early education. This channel is intended to be fully COPPA compliant.
